            <span>HELOC Calculator</span>
        </nav>

        <!-- Calculator card -->
        <section class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md" aria-labelledby="calc-title">
          <h1 id="calc-title" class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-2 text-slate-800">HELOC Calculator</h1>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Estimate your maximum HELOC line (by CLTV), interest-only draw payment, amortized repayment payment, CLTV after draw, and total interest. Includes a balance chart and CSV export.</p>

          <!-- Inputs -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="homeValue">Home value *</label>
              <div class="relative">
                <input id="homeValue" type="number" inputmode="decimal" min="0" step="0.01" placeholder="e.g., 500000" class="form-control" aria-describedby="err-homeValue" aria-required="true">
                <span class="input-unit">$</span>
              </div>
              <p id="err-homeValue" class="error min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="mortgageBalance">Current mortgage balance *</label>
              <div class="relative">
                <input id="mortgageBalance" type="number" inputmode="decimal" min="0" step="0.01" placeholder="e.g., 300000" class="form-control" aria-describedby="err-mortgage" aria-required="true">
                <span class="input-unit">$</span>
              </div>
              <p id="err-mortgage" class="error min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="cltvLimit">Max combined LTV (CLTV) *</label>
              <div class="relative">
                <input id="cltvLimit" type="number" inputmode="decimal" min="50" max="100" step="1" value="85" class="form-control" aria-describedby="err-cltv" aria-required="true">
                <span class="input-unit">%</span>
              </div>
              <p id="err-cltv" class="error min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="drawAmount">Desired initial draw *</label>
              <div class="relative">
                <input id="drawAmount" type="number" inputmode="decimal" min="0" step="0.01" placeholder="e.g., 50000" class="form-control" aria-describedby="err-draw" aria-required="true">
                <span class="input-unit">$</span>
              </div>
              <p id="err-draw" class="error min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="drawYears">Draw period (years) *</label>
              <input id="drawYears" type="number" inputmode="numeric" min="0" max="20" step="1" value="10" class="form-control" aria-describedby="err-drawYears" aria-required="true">
              <p id="err-drawYears" class="error min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="repayYears">Repayment term (years) *</label>
              <input id="repayYears" type="number" inputmode="numeric" min="1" max="30" step="1" value="20" class="form-control" aria-describedby="err-repayYears" aria-required="true">
              <p id="err-repayYears" class="error min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="drawApr">APR during draw *</label>
              <div class="relative">
                <input id="drawApr" type="number" inputmode="decimal" min="0" max="100" step="0.01" value="8.25" class="form-control" aria-describedby="err-drawApr" aria-required="true">
                <span class="input-unit">%</span>
              </div>
              <p id="err-drawApr" class="error min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="repayApr">APR during repayment *</label>
                <label class="text-sm text-gray-700">
                  <input id="sameRate" type="checkbox" checked class="mr-1"> Same as draw
                </label>
              </div>
              <div class="relative">
                <input id="repayApr" type="number" inputmode="decimal" min="0" max="100" step="0.01" value="8.25" class="form-control" aria-describedby="err-repayApr" aria-required="true">
                <span class="input-unit">%</span>
              </div>
              <p id="err-repayApr" class="error min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Actions -->
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-4 actions">
            <button id="calcBtn" type="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center min-h-[44px] px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">Calculate</button>
            <button id="resetBtn" type="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center min-h-[44px] px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-blue-600 text-blue-700 font-semibold hover:bg-blue-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">Reset</button>
            <button id="renderChartBtn" type="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center min-h-[44px] px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 font-semibold hover:bg-gray-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">Render chart</button>
            <button id="downloadCsvBtn" type="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center min-h-[44px] px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 font-semibold hover:bg-gray-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">Download CSV</button>
          </div>

          <!-- Results -->
          <div id="results" class="mt-8 bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">Results</h2>

            <div class="result-grid">
              <div class="result-item"><span class="result-label">Maximum HELOC line</span><span id="maxLineValue" class="result-value">$0.00</span></div>
              <div class="result-item"><span class="result-label">CLTV after draw</span><span id="cltvAfterValue" class="result-value">0.00%</span></div>
              <div class="result-item"><span class="result-label">Draw payment (interest-only)</span><span id="drawPaymentValue" class="result-value">$0.00</span></div>
              <div class="result-item"><span class="result-label">Repayment payment (amortized)</span><span id="repayPaymentValue" class="result-value">$0.00</span></div>
              <div class="result-item"><span class="result-label">Total interest (draw + repayment)</span><span id="totalInterestValue" class="result-value">$0.00</span></div>
              <div class="result-item"><span class="result-label">Feasibility</span><span id="feasibilityValue" class="result-value"><span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded-full border text-sm bg-yellow-50 border-yellow-200 text-yellow-800">Awaiting inputs</span></span></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Chart -->
            <div class="mt-4 bg-white border border-blue-100 rounded-lg p-4">
              <canvas id="balanceChart" height="120" aria-label="Balance over time chart"></canvas>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SEO content (kept & polished) -->
        <article class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md mt-8 prose">
          <h2>Data Source and Methodology</h2>
          <p><strong>Authoritative Data Source:</strong> OpenStax, <em>Algebra and Trigonometry</em>, Section 6.8 “The Mathematics of Finance” (amortization formulas). All payment and total interest calculations follow these standard formulas. For product context on HELOCs, see CFPB’s overview of how HELOCs work.</p>

          <h2>The Formula Explained</h2>
          <div class="formula-box" aria-label="Mathematical formulas">
            <div><strong>Maximum line:</strong> \( L_{\max} = \max\!\big(0,\ \text{CLTV}_{\max}\cdot V - M \big) \)</div>
            <div style="margin-top:.5rem;"><strong>CLTV after draw:</strong> \( \text{CLTV}_{\text{after}} = \dfrac{M + D}{V} \)</div>
            <div style="margin-top:.5rem;"><strong>Interest-only during draw:</strong> \( I_{\text{draw,m}} = D \cdot \dfrac{r_d}{12} \)</div>
            <div style="margin-top:.5rem;"><strong>Repayment payment:</strong> \( P = \dfrac{(r_r/12)\,B}{1 - (1 + r_r/12)^{-n}} \) with \(B=D\) at repayment start</div>
            <div style="margin-top:.5rem;"><strong>Total interest:</strong> \( I_{\text{total}} = I_{\text{draw,m}}\cdot n_d + (P\cdot n_r - B) \)</div>
          </div>

          <h2>How It Works: Example</h2>
          <ol>
            <li>\(L_{\max} = 0.85\cdot 500{,}000 - 300{,}000 = 125{,}000\)</li>
            <li>\(\text{CLTV}_{\text{after}} = (300{,}000 + 50{,}000)/500{,}000 = 70\%\)</li>
            <li>Draw payment: \(50{,}000 \times 0.0825/12 \approx \$343.75\)</li>
            <li>Repayment payment: \( \approx \$427.39 \) for \(r=0.0825\), \(n=240\)</li>
            <li>Total interest: \(\approx \$93{,}823.60\)</li>
          </ol>

          <h2>FAQs</h2>
          <p><strong>Do rates change?</strong> Many HELOCs have variable rates. Model different draw and repayment rates using the separate APR fields.</p>
          <p><strong>Are payments during draw interest-only?</strong> Often yes. Some agreements allow principal payments during draw—check your contract.</p>
          <p><strong>Are fees and taxes included?</strong> No; closing costs, caps, and taxes are excluded in this idealized model.</p>

          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 border-t pt-4">
            Tool developed by <strong>Ugo Candido</strong>. Content verified by the <strong>CalcDomain Editorial Team</strong>.<br/>
            Last reviewed: September 13, 2025.
          </div>
        </article>
      </main>

      <!-- Right: Sidebar -->
      <aside class="w-full lg:w-1/3">
        <div class="sticky top-24">
          <div class="bg-gray-200 h-96 rounded-lg mb-6 flex items-center justify-center no-print">
            <p class="text-gray-500">Sticky Ad Unit (e.g., 300×600)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">Related Finance Tools</h3>
